      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YEAH YOU (4) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 19.70 beating Suave. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. WILD VENUS (8) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 1.3 lengths (19.78) behind YEAH YOU at this track. Has won two of four starts from this draw. Likely to be in the finish again. KING CHERRY (7) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (19.56) at this track in a Grade 5. Can turn it around this time. DEMON KYSAIAH (2) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
